hadiths[115]{hadithnumber,text}:
965,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ko koi kaanta bhi chubtaa hai, ya us sey bhi kam koi takleef pahunchti hai to Allah Taala uski wajeh sey uska eik darja buland aur uskey badley uska eik gunah maaf kar deta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad bin Abi Waqas , abu-Ubaida bin Jarrah , Abu-Hurera , abu-Umama , abu Saeed Khudri , Anas , Abdullah bin Amr bin al-Aas , Asad bin Kurz, Jabir bin Abdullah , Abdur-Rehman bin Azhar aur Abu-Musa Ash-ari (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
966,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ko jo bhi takaan, gham, aur bimari yahan tak key fikr laahiq hoti hai to Allah Taala uskey badley uskey gunah mita deta hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz logon ney ye hadees b-tareeq : « Ata bin Yasar an abi Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) an Nabi sallallahu Alehi wasallam » riwayat ki hai, 3- Wakee kehtey hain : is hadees key ilawa kisi hadees mein « همّ » '' fikr '' key barey mein nahin suna gaya ke wo bhi gunahon ka kaffara hota hai."
967,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''musalman jab apney musalman bhai ki iyaadat karta hai to wo barabar jannat mein phal chuntaa rehta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Soban ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Abu Ghaffar aur Aasim Ahwal ney ye hadees ba-tareeq : (an Abi Qulaba an abi Ash,as an abi Asma an Soban an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat ki hai. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke jisney ye hadees b-tareeq : (an abi Ash'as an abi Asmaa) riwayat ki hai wo ziyada sahih hai. 4- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : abu-Qulaba ki hadisein abu-Asmaa hi sey marvi hain siwaye is hadees key ye merey nazdik ba-tareeq : (an abi Ash'as an abi Asmaa) marvi hai. 5- is bab mein Ali , abu-Musa , Bara , Abu-Hurera , Anas aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
968,"Soban (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai, albatta is mein itna izafa hai : arz kiya gaya : jannat ka khurfa kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''uskey phal todnaa.'' eik dusri sanad sey Ayub sey aur Ayub ney abu-Qulaba sey , aur abu-Qulaba ney abu-Asmaa sey , aur abu-Asmaa ney Soban sey aur Soban ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey Khalid ki hadees ki tarah riwayat ki hai, aur is mein Ahmed bin Abda ney abu-Ash'ash key wastey ka zikr nahin kiya hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : baaz ney ye hadees Hammad bin Zaid sey riwayat ki hai lekin isey marfoo nahin kiya hai."
969,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney mera haath pakad kar kaha : hamarey sath Hasan key paas chalo hum un ki iyaadat karengey to hamney unkey paas abu-Musa ko paya. to Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney puchha : Abu-Musa kya aap iyaadat key liye aaye hain? ya ziyaarat « شماتت » key liye? to unhoney kaha : nahin, balke iyaadat key liye aaya hun. is par Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jo musalman bhi kisi musalman ki subah key waqt iyaadat karta hai to Sham tak sattar hazar farishtey uskey liye istighfar kartey hain. aur jo Sham ko iyaadat karta hai to subah tak sattar hazar farishtey uskey liye istighfar kartey hain. aur uskey liye jannat main eik baagh hoga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees kaee aur bhi turq sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, in mein sey baaz ney moqufan aur baaz ney marfooan riwayat ki hai."
970,"Main Khubab bin Arat (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaya, unkey pet mein aag sey dagh key nishaanaat they, to unhoney kaha : nahin janta ke Sahaba mein kisi ney itni musibat jhaili ho jo mainey jhaili hai, Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key ehad mein merey paas eik dirham bhi nahin hota tha, jabke is waqt merey ghar key eik koney mein chaalis hazar dirham padey hain, agar Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hamein maut ki tamanna karney sey na roka hota to main maut ki tamanna zarur karta. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Khubab (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas , Abu-Hurera , aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
971,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum mein sey koi hergiz kisi musibat ki wajeh sey jo is par nazil hui ho maut ki tamanna na karey. balke wo yun kahey : « اللهم أحيني ما كانت الحياة خيرا لي وتوفني إذا كانت الوفاة خيرا لي » ''aey Allah ! mujhey zinda rakh jab tak ke zindagi merey liye behtar ho, aur mujhey maut dey jab merey liye maut behtar ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
972,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas aa kar Jibreel ney puchha : aey Muhammad ! kya aap bimar hain? farmaya : haan , Jibreel ney kaha : (باسم الله أرقيك من كل شيء يؤذيك من شر كل نفس وعين حاسد باسم الله أرقيك والله يشفيك) ''Main Allah key naam sey aap par dam karta hun har us chiz sey jo aap ko izaa (takleef) pahuncha rahi hai, har nafs key shar sey aur har haasid ki aankh sey , main Allah key naam sey aap par dam karta hun, Allah aap ko shifaa ata farmaeyga.''"
973,"Main aur Sabit Bunani dono Anas bin Malik (Raziallahu anhu) key paas gaey. Sabit ney kaha : abu-Hamza ! main bimar ho gaya hun, Anas ney kaha : kya main tum par Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key mantr key zariey dam na kar dun? unhoney kaha : kyon nahin ! Anas ney kaha : (اللهم رب الناس مذهب الباس اشف أنت الشافي لا شافي إلا أنت شفاء لا يغادر سقما)''aey Allah ! logon key rab ! musibat ko door karney waley ! shifaa ata farma , tu hi shifaa deney wala hai, terey siwa koi shaafi nahin, aisi shifaa dey ke koi bimari baqi na reh jaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- mainey abu-Zara'a sey is hadees key barey mein puchha ke Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ki riwayat basanad : (abi Nazar an abi Saeed Khudr) ziyada sahih hai ya Abdul-Azeez ki Anas sey riwayat hai? to unhoney kaha : dono sahih hain. 3- Abdus-Samad bin Abdul-Waaris ney basanad (Abdul-Waaris an Abeeh an Abdul Azeez bin Suheb an Abi Nazar an abi Saeed) riwayat ki hai aur Abdul-Azeez bin Suheb ney Anas sey bhi riwayat ki hai. 4- is bab mein Anas aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
974,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''eik musalman , jiski do raaten bhi is haal mein guzrin ke uskey paas wasiyat karney ki koi chiz ho, is par lazim hai ke uski wasiyat uskey paas likhi hui ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abi Aufi (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadees aai hai."
975,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney meri iyaadat farmaee, main bimar tha. to aap ney puchha : kya tum ney wasiyat kar di hai? mainey arz kiya : ji haan (kar di hai), aap ney farmaya : ''kitney ki? ''main ney arz kya : Allah ki raah mein apney sarey maal ki. aap ney puchha : ''apni aulad key liye tum ney kya chhoda? ''maine arz kiya : wo maal sey be niyaz hain, aap ney farmaya : ''daswen hissey ki wasiyat karo.'' to main barabar isey ziyada karata raha yahan tak ke aap ney farmaya : ''tihai maal ki wasiyat karo, aur tihai bhi ziyada hai.'' abu-Abdur-Rehman (Nasaaee) kehtey hain : hum log Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key is farman ki wajeh sey ke tihai maal ki wasiyat bhi ziyada hai mustahab yehi samajhtey hain ke tihai sey bhi kam ki wasiyat ki jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Saad (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Saad (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye hadees doosrey aur turq sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi riwayat hai, aur in sey « والثلث كثير » ki jagah « والثلث كبير » ''tihai badi miqdaar hai'' bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, 4- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, wo is baat ko sahih qarar nahin detey ke aadmi tihai sey ziyada ki wasiyat karey aur mustahab samajhtey hain ke tihai sey kam ki wasiyat karey. 5- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : log chothai hissey key muqabil mein paanchwen hissey ko aur tihai key muqabley mein chothai hissey ko mustahab samajhtey they, aur kehtey they ke jisney tihai ki wasiyat kar di usney kuchh nahin chhoda. aur uskey liye tihai sey ziyada jayez nahin."
976,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney marney waley logon ko jo bilkul marney key qarib hon (لا إله إلا الله) ki talqin padhi. karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri ki hadees Hasan gharib sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Abu-Hurera , Umme-Salma , Aaisha , Jabir , Sa'dii Murriya (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- Sa'dii Murriya Talha bin Ubedullah ki biwi hain."
977,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum sey farmaya : ''jab tum mareez key paas ya kisi marey huye aadmi key paas aao to achchhi baat kaho, isliye ke jo tum kehtey ho is par Malaaika 'Aameen' kehtey hain.''  jab Abu-Salma ka intiqal huwa, to mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke paas aa kar arz kiya : Allah ke Rasool ! Abu-Salma ka intiqal ho gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : to tum ye dua padho : «اللهم اغفر لي وله وأعقبني منه عقبى حسنة»''aey Allah ! mujhey aur unhen maaf farma dey, aur mujhey unka behatreen badal ata farma. ''wo kehti hain ke : jab mainey ye dua padhi to Allah ney mujhey aisi hasti ata kar di jo un sey behtar thi yani Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko ata kiya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme-Salma (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye mustahab samjha jata tha ke mareez ko uski maut key waqt «لا إله إلا الله» ki talqin ki jaey. 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : jab wo (maiyat) isey eik baar keh dey aur uskey baad phir na boley to munasib nahin ke uskey samney baar-baar ye kalima dohraya jaey. 4- ibne-Mubarak key barey mein marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke jab unki maut ka waqt aaya, to eik shakhs unhen «لا إله إلا الله» ki talqin karney laga aur baar-baar karney laga, Abdullah bin Mubarak ney us sey kaha : jab tum ney eik baar keh diya to main ab isi par qaaim hun jab tak koi aur guftgu na karun, Abdullah key is qol ka matlab ye hai ke un ki murad is sey wohi thi jo Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke ''jis ka aakhiri qol «لا إله إلا الله» ho to wo jannat mein dakhil hoga.''"
978,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap sakhti key aalim mein they, aap key paas eik piyala tha, jis mein pani tha, aap piyaley mein apna haath daltey phir apney chehrey par maltey aur farmatey : (اللهم أعني على غمرات الموت أو سكرات الموت) ''aey Allah ! maut ki sakhti mein meri madad farma.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
979,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki maut ki jo shiddat mainey dekhi , uskey baad main kisi ki jaan aasani sey nikalney par rashk nahin karti. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : mainey Abu-Zara'a sey is hadees key barey mein puchha ke Abdur-Rehman bin Alaa kon hain? to unhoney kaha : wo Alaa bin Lajlaj hain, main isey isi tareeqe sey janta hun."
980,Mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''momin ki jaan thoda thoda kar key nikalti hai jaisey jism sey paseena nikalta hai aur mujhey gadhey jaisi maut pasand nahin.'' arz kiya gaya : gadhey ki maut kya hai? aap ney farmaya : ''achanak maut''.
981,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab bhi dono likhney waley (farishtey) din aur raat kisi key amal ko likh kar Allah key paas ley jatey hain aur Allah Taala daftar key shuru aur akheer mein khair (nek kaam) likha huwa paata hai to farmata hai : ''main tum logon ko gawah banata hun ke mainey apney bandey key sarey gunah maaf kar diey jo is daftar key dono kinaron shuru aur akheer ke darmiyan mein hain.''
982,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin peshani key paseene key sath martaa hai.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke hamein Abdullah bin Barida sey Qatada key samaa (suna), ka ilm nahin hai."
983,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik nojawan key paas aaye aur wo sakhti key aalim mein tha. aap ney farmaya : ''tum apney ko kaisa paa rahey ho?'' usney arz kiya : Allah ki qism , Allah key Rasool ! mujhey Allah sey ummid hai aur apney gunahon sey dar bhi raha hun, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''ye dono cheezen is jaisey waqt mein jis bandey key dil mein jama ho jati hain to Allah usey wo chiz ata kar deta hai jiski wo us sey ummid rakhta hai aur usey us chiz sey mehfooz rakhta hai jis sey wo dar raha hota hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan aur gharib hai. 2- aur baaz logon ney ye hadees Sabit sey aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mursalan riwayat ki hai."
984,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''«نعی» (maut ki khabar deney) padhi. sey bacho, kyonkey «نعی» jahiliyat ka amal hai.'' Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) kehtey hain : «نعی» ka matlab maiyat ki maut ka aelan hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein Huzefa (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai,"
985,"Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey isi tarah marvi (riwayat hui) hai, aur Raavi ney isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. aur usney is mein iska bhi zikr nahin kiya hai ke ''«نعی» maut key aelan ka naam hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- ye Anbasaa ki hadees sey jisey unhoney Abu-Hamza sey riwayat kiya hai ziyada sahih hai. 3- abu-Hamza hi Memun Aa'war hain, ye ehale hadees key nazdik qawi nahin hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm ney «نعی» ko makrooh qarar diya hai, unkey nazdik «نعی» ye hai ke logon mein aelan kiya jaey ke falan mar gaya hai taake uskey janaazey mein shirkat karen. 5- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : is mein koi harj nahin ke uskey rishtey daaron aur uskey bhaiyon ko uskey marney ki khabar di jaey. 6- Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke is mein koi harj nahin ke aadmi ko uskey apney kisi qurbat daar key marney ki khabar di jaey."
986,unhoney kaha : jab main mar jaaun to tum merey marney ka aelan mat karna. mujhey dar hai ke ye baat «نعی» hogi. kyonkey mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko «نعی» sey mana farmatey suna hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
987,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sabr wohi hai jo pehley sadmey key waqt ho.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees is sanad sey gharib hai.
988,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sabr wohi hai jo pehley sadme ke waqt ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
989,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Usman bin Mazoon (Raziallahu anhu) ka bosa liya. wo intiqal kar chukey they. aap ro rahey they. ya (Raavi ney) kaha : aap ki dono aankhen aasunoon se bhari thin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , Jabir aur Aaisha sey bhi hadeesen aai hain, wo kehtey hain ke abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka bosa liya padhi. aur aap intiqal farma chukey they."
990,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki eik beti padhi. ka intiqal ho gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''isey taaq baar ghusl do, teen baar ya paanch baar ya is sey ziyada baar, agar zaruri samjho aur pani aur bair ki patti sey ghusl do , aakhir mein kaafur mila lena.''  ya farmaya : ''thoda sa kaafur mila lena aur jab tum ghusl sey farigh ho jaao to mujhey ittilaa dena.''  chunanche jab hum (nahlakar) farigh ho gaey, to hamney aap ko ittilaa di, aap ney apna tehband hamari taraf dal diya aur farmaya : ''isey iskey badan sey lapet do.'' Hasheem kehtey hain ke aur doosrey logon padhi. ki riwaayaton mein, mujhey nahin malum shayad Hisham bhi unhi mein sey hon, ye hai ke unhoney kaha : aur hamney inke baalon ko teen chotiyon mein goondh diya. Hasheem kehtey hain : mera guman hai ke unki riwaayaton mein ye bhi hai ke phir hamney un chotiyon ko unkey peechhey dal diya Hasheem kehtey hain : phir Khalid ney hum sey logon key samney bayan kiya wo Hafsa aur Muhammad sey riwayat kar rahey they aur ye dono Umme Atiya (Raziallahu Anha) sey ke wo kehti hain ke hum sey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''pehley inkey dahiney sey aur wuzu ke aaza (ango) sey shuru karna.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Umme Atiya (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Umme Sulem (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. 4- Ibrahim Nakhai kehtey hain ke maiyat ka ghusl ghusle-janabat (sambhog ke baad ka ghusl) ki tarah hai. 5- Malik bin Anas kehtey hain : hamarey nazdik maiyat key ghusl ki koi mutayyan had nahin aur na hi koi mutayyan kaifiyat hai, bas usey pak kar diya jaeyga. 6- Shafai kehtey hain ke Malik ka qol ke usey ghusl diya jaey aur paak kiya jaey mujmal hai, jab maiyat beeri ya kisi aur chiz key pani sey paak kar diya jaey to bas itna kafi hai, albatta merey nazdik mustahab ye hai ke isey teen ya is sey ziyada baar ghusl diya jaey. teen baar sey kam ghusl na diya jaey, isliye ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai'' isey teen baar ya paanch baar ghusl do.''  aur agar log usey teen sey kam martaba main hi pak saaf kar den to ye bhi kafi hai, hum ye nahin samajhtey hain ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka teen ya paanch baar ka hukm dena mehaz paak karney key liye hai, aap ney koi had muqarrar nahin ki hai, aisey hi doosrey fuqaha ney bhi kaha hai. wo hadees key mafhoom ko khub janney waley hain. 7- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : har martaba ghusl pani aur beeri ki patti sey hoga, albatta aakhiri baar us-mein kaafur mila leingey."
991,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''sab sey behtareen khushbu mushk hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
992,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey mushk key barey mein puchha gaya to aap ney farmaya : ''ye tumhari khushbuon mein sab sey behtar khushbu hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- aur isey Mustamir bin Rayyan ney bhi ba-tareeq : (abi Nazar an Abi Saeed an Nabi Sallallahu Alehi wasallam) riwayat kiya hai, Yahya bin Saeed kehtey hain ke Mustamir bin Rayyan bharosemand hain. 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm ney maiyat key liye mushk ko makrooh qarar diya hai."
993,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maiyat ko nahlaaney sey ghusl aur usey uthaney sey wuzu hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai. 2- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) sey ye moqufan bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai, 3- is bab mein Ali aur Aaisha Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- ehle-ilm ka us shakhs key barey mein ikhtilaf hai jo maiyat ko ghusl dey. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke jab koi kisi maiyat ko ghusl dey to is par ghusl hai. 5- baaz kehtey hain is par wuzu hai. Maalik bin Anas kehtey hain : maiyat ko ghusl deney sey ghusl karna merey nazdik mustahab hai, main isey wajib nahin samajhta isi tarah Shafai ka bhi qol hai. 6- Ahmed kehtey hain : jisney maiyat ko ghusl diya to mujhey ummid hai ke is par ghusl wajib nahin hoga. rahi wuzu ki baat to ye sab sey kam hai jo is silsiley mein kaha gaya hai. 7- Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : wuzu zaruri hai padhi. , Abdullah bin Mubarak sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai ke unhoney kaha ke jisney maiyat ko ghusl diya, wo na ghusl karega na wuzu."
994,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum safed kapdey pahno, kyonkey ye tumharey behtareen kapdon mein sey hain aur isi mein apney mardon ko bhi kafnaao.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Samura, ibne-Umar aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- aur ehle-ilm isi ko mustahab qarar detey hain. ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : merey nazdik mustahab ye hai ke aadmi unhi kapdon mein kafnaya jaey jin mein wo namaz padhta tha. 4- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : kafnaaney key liye merey nazdik sab sey pasandida kapda safed rang ka kapda hai. aur achchha kafan dena mustahab hai."
995,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum mein koi apney bhai ka (kafan key silsiley mein) wali (zimme-daar) ho to usey achchha kafan dey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain ke Salam bin Abi Muteea' aap key qol : « وليحسن أحدكم كفن أخيه » ''apney bhai ko achchha kafan do'' key barey mein kehtey hain ke is sey murad kapdey ki safai aur safedi hai, is sey qeemti kapda murad nahin hai."
996,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko teen safed Yamni kapdon mein kafnaaya gaya padhi. na un mein qamis padhi. thi aur na amaamaa. logon ney Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey kaha : log kehtey hain ke aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko do kapdon aur eik dhaari daar chadar mein kafnaaya gaya tha? to Ummul-momenin Aaisha ney kaha : chadar laee gaee thi lekin logon ney isey wapis kar diya tha, aap ko is mein nahin kafnaaya gaya tha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
997,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Hamza bin Abdul-Muttalib (Raziallahu anhu) ko eik hi kapdey main eik chadar mein kafnaaya. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ke kafan ke barey mein mukhtalif hadeesen aai hain. aur in sabhi hadeeson mein Aaisha wali hadees sab sey ziyada sahih hai. 3- is bab mein Ali padhi. , ibne-Abbas , Abdullah bin Mughaffal aur ibne-Umar (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka amal Aaisha hi ki hadees par hai. 5- Sufiyan Sory kehtey hain : aadmi ko teen kapdon mein kafnaaya jaey. chahey eik qamis aur do lifafon mein , aur chahey teen lifafon mein. agar do kapdey na milen to eik bhi kafi hai, aur do kapdey bhi kafi ho jatey hain, aur jisey teen muyassar hon to uskey liye mustahab yehi teen kapdey hain. Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. wo kehtey hain : aurat ko paanch kapdon mein kafnaya jaey."
998,"jab Jaafar Taiyaar key marney ki khabar aai padhi. to Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''Jaafar key ghar walon key liye khana pakaao, isliye ke aaj unkey paas aisi chiz aai hai jis mein wo mashghool hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- baaz ehle-ilm maiyat key ghar walon key musibat mein phasey honey ki wajeh sey un ke yahan kuchh bhejney ko mustahab qarar detey hain. yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai. 3- Jaafar bin Khalid ke walid Khalid Saara ke betey hain aur bharosemand hain. in sey ibne-Jurej ney riwayat ki hai."
999,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo gireban phaadey, chehra peetey aur jahiliyat ki haank pukarey padhi. hum mein sey nahin.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1000,"Ansaar ka Qurzaa bin Kaab Naami eik shakhs mar gaya, is par nauha padhi. kiya gaya to Mughira bin Shoba (Raziallahu anhu) aaye aur member par chadhey. aur Allah ki hamd aur sanaa bayan ki phir kaha : kya baat hai? Islam mein nauha ho raha hai. suno ! mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : ''jis par nauha kiya gaya is par nauha kiye janey ka azab hoga.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Mughira ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein umr , Ali , abu-Musa , Qais bin Aasim , Abu-Hurera , Junaada bin Malik , Anas , Umme Atiya , Samura aur abu Malik Ash-ari (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1001,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''meri ummat mein chaar baaten jahiliyat ki hain, log unhen kabhi nahin chodengey : nauha karna, hasab aur nasab mein taana zani, aur bimari ka eik sey doosrey ko lag janey ka aqeeda rakhna maslan yun kehna ke eik oont ko khujli hui aur usney sau oont mein khujli phela di to aakhir pehley oont ko khujli kaise kaisey lagi? aur nakchhatron ka aqeeda rakhna. maslan falan aur falan (sitarey) ke sabab hum par barish hui.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1002,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maiyat ko uskey ghar walon key is par roney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- umr (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Umar aur Imran bin Husain (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 3- ehle-ilm ki eik jamaat ney maiyat par roney ko makrooh (tehrimi) qarar diya hai. wo kehtey hain ke maiyat ko is par roney ki wajeh sey azab diya jata hai. aur wo isi hadees ki taraf gaey hain. 4- aur ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : mujhey ummid hai ke agar wo (maiyat) apni zindagi mein logon ko is sey rokta raha ho to is par is mein sey kuchh nahin hoga.
1003,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo koi bhi mar jaey phir is par roney wala khada ho kar kahey : haaye merey pahad , haaye merey sardar ya is jaisey alfaz kahey to usey do farishton key hawaley kar diya jata hai, wo usey ghoonsey maartey hain (aur kehtey jatey hain) kya to aisa hi tha?'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1004,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''maiyat ko apney ghar walon key is par roney sey azab diya jata hai.'' Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) kehti hain : Allah (ibne-Umar) par reham karey, unhoney jhoot nahin kaha, unhen weham huwa hai. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney to ye baat us Yahudi key liye farmaee thi jo mar gaya tha : ''maiyat ko azab ho raha hai aur uskey ghar waley is par ro rahey hain.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- ye hadees dusri sanadon sey bhi Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai. 3- is bab mein ibne-Abbas, Qurza bin Kaab , Abu-Hurera , ibne-Masood aur Usama bin Zaid (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. 4- baaz ehle-ilm isi janib gaey hain aur un logon ney aayat : «ولا تزر وازرة وزر أخرى » ''koi kisi ka bojh nahin uthaey ga.''  ka matlab bhi yehi bayan kiya hai aur yehi Shafai ka bhi qol hai."
1005,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ka haath pakda aur unhen apney betey Ibrahim key paas ley gaey to dekha ke Ibrahim ka aakhiri waqt hai, Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Ibrahim ko utha kar apni god mein rakh liya aur ro diye. Abdur-Rehman bin Auf ney kaha : kya aap ro rahey hain? kya aap ney roney se mana nahin kiya tha? to aap ney farmaya : ''nahin, main to do ahmaq faajir (badkaar) aawaazon sey rokta tha : eik to musibat key waqt aawaz nikalney, chehra zakhmi karney sey aur gireban phadney sey, doosrey shetan key naghmey sey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan hai."
1006,"Unhoney Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ko kehtey suna aur un sey zikr kiya gaya tha ke ibne-Umar Raziallahu anhuma kehtey hain ke maiyat par logon key roney ki wajeh sey usey azab diya jata hai (Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney kaha) Allah abu-Abdur-Rehman ki maghfirat farmaey. suno, unhoney jhoot nahin kaha. balke un sey bhool hui hai ya wo chook gaey hain. baat sirf itni thi ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ka guzar eik Yahudi aurat key paas sey huwa jis par log ro rahey they. to aap ney farmaya : ''ye log is par ro rahey hain aur usey qabr mein azab diya ja raha hai.''"
1007,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar aur umr sab ko janaazey ke aagey aagey chaltey dekha hai."
1008,"Mainey Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma sab ko janaazey key aagey aagey chaltey dekha hai."
1009,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , abu-Bakar aur umr Raziallahu anhuma janaazey ke aagey aagey chaltey they. Zohri ye bhi kehtey hain ke mujhey Salim bin Abdullah ney khabar di ke un ke walid Abdullah bin umr janaazey key aagey chaltey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abdullah bin umr Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees isi tarah hai, isey ibne-Jurej, Ziyad bin Saad aur deegar kaee logon ney Zohri sey ibne Uena ki hadees hi ki tarah riwayat kiya hai, aur Zohri ney Salim bin Abdullah sey aur Salim ney apney walid ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai. Maamar, Yunus bin Yazeed aur haafizon mein sey aur bhi kaee logon ney Zohri sey riwayat ki hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam janaazey key aagey chaltey they. Zohri kehtey hain ke mujhey Salim bin Abdullah ney khabar di hai ke unkey walid janaazey key aagey chaltey they. tamam muhaddeseen ki raey hai ke mursal hadees hi is baab mein ziyada sahih hai 2- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain ke is silsiley mein Zohri ki hadees mursal hai, aur ibne Uena ki hadees sey ziyada sahih hai. 3- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain ke mera khayal hai ke ibne-Jurej ney ye hadees ibn Uena sey li hai. 4- Hamaam bin Yahya ney ye hadees Ziyad bin Saad , Mansoor , Bakr aur Sufiyan sey aur un logon ney Zohri sey , Zohri ney Salim bin Abdullah sey aur Salim ney apney walid ibne-Umar sey riwayat ki hai. aur Sufiyan sey murad Sufiyan bin Uena hain jin sey Hamaam ney riwayat ki hai. 5- is bab mein Anas (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi riwayat hai, Anas ki hadees is baab mein ghair mehfooz hai. 6- janaazey key aagey chalney mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai. Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke janaazey key aagey chalna afzal hai. Shafai aur Ahmed isi key qaail hain."
1010,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam , Abu-Bakar , umr aur Usman (Raziallauh anhum) janaazey key aagey chaltey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein poochha, to unhoney kaha : ye hadees ghalat hai is mein Muhammad bin Bakr ney ghalati ki hai. ye hadees Yunus sey riwayat ki jati hai, aur Yunus Zohri sey (mursalan) riwayat kartey hain ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam, Abu-Bakar aur umr janaazey key aagey chaltey they. Zohri kehtey hain : mujhey Salim bin Abdullah ney khabar di hai ke unke walid janaazey ke aagey aagey chaltey they. 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : ye ziyada sahih hai. (dekhiye sabiqa (pichhli) hadees 1009.)"
1011,"hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey janaazey key peechhey chalney key barey mein puchha to aap ney farmaya : ''aisi chaal chaley jo dulki chaal sey dheemi ho. agar wo nek hai to tum usey jaldi qabr mein pahuncha dogey aur agar bura hai to jahannamiyon hi ko door hataayaa jata hai. janaza key peechhey chalna chahiye, us sey aagey nahin hona chahiye, jo janaze ke aagey chaley wo uskey sath janey walon mein sey nahin.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Abdullah bin Masood sey sirf isi sanad sey jaani jati hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko Abu Haamid ki is hadees ko zaeef batatey suna hai. 3- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ka bayan hai ke Humedi kehtey hain ke Sufiyan bin Uena kehtey hain ke Yahya bin Moayan sey puchha gaya : Abu Maajid kon hain? to unhoney kaha : eik udti chidiyaa hai jis sey hamney riwayat ki hai, yani majhool Raavi hai."
1012,"Hum Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath eik janaazey mein nikley, aap ney kuch logon ko sawar dekha to farmaya : ''kya tumhen sharam nahin aati? Allah key farishtey pedal chal rahey hain aur tum janweron ki peethon par bethey ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Soban ki hadees , in sey moqufan bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain : inki maqoof riwayat ziyada sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Mughira bin Shoba aur Jabir bin Samura Raziallahu anhuma sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1013,"Hum log Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key sath Abu Deh-Daah key janaazey mein they, aap laut'tey waqt eik ghodey par sawar they jo tez chal raha tha, hum uskey ird-gird they aur wo aap ko ley kar uchhaltey huye chal raha tha."
1014,Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Abu Deh-Daah key janaza key peechhey pedal gaey aur ghodey par sawar ho kar lotey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai.
1015,"Janaza tezi sey ley kar chalo, agar wo nek hoga to usey khair ki taraf jaldi pahuncha dogey, aur agar wo bura hoga to usey apni gardan sey utaar kar (jald) rakh dogey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Bakra sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1016,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uhad key din Hamza (ki laash) key paas aaye. aap uskey paas rukey, aap ney dekha ke laash ka musla kar diya gaya hai. aap ney farmaya : ''agar Safiya (Hamza ki behan) apney dil mein bura na maantin to main unhen yun hi (dafn kiye baghair) chhod deta yahan tak ke parinde aur darinde unhen kha jatey. phir wo qiyamat key din unke peton sey uthaey jatey.''  phir aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney «namr» (eik purani chadar) mangwaai aur Hamza ko is mein kafnaaya jab aap chadar unkey sar ki taraf khinchtey to unkey dono pair khul jatey aur jab unke dono pairon ki taraf khinchtey to sar khul jata. maqtooleen ki tadaad badh gaee aur kapdey kam pad gaey they, chunanche eik eik do-do aur teen-teen aadmiyon ko eik kapdey mein kafnaaya jata, phir wo sab eik qabr mein dafn kar diye jatey. Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam unkey barey mein poochhtey ke un mein kis ko Quran ziyada yad tha to aap usey aagey qibley ki taraf kar detey, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un maqtooleen ko dafn kiya aur un par namaz nahin padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. hum isey Anas ki riwayat sey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 2- is hadees ki riwayat mein Usama bin Zaid ki mukhalifat ki gaee hai. Les bin Saad basanad (an ibne Shahaab an Abdur-Rehman bin Ka'aab bin Maalik an Jabir bin Abdullah bin Zaid) riwayat ki hai aur Maamar ney basanad (an Zohri an Abdullah bin Saulba an Jabir) riwayat ki hai. hamarey ilm mein siwaye Usama bin Zaid key koi aisa shakhs nahin hai jisney Zohri key wastey sey Anas sey riwayat ki ho. 3- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari sey is hadees key barey mein puchha to unhoney kaha : Les ki hadees basanad (an ibne Shahaab an Abdur-Rehman bin Ka'aab bin Maalik an Jabir) ziyada sahih hai. 4- namra : purani chadar ko kehtey hain."
1017,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mareez ki iyaadat kartey , janaazey mein shareek hotey , gadhey ki sawari kartey aur ghulam ki dawat qubul farmatey they. banu Qureza padhi. waley din aap eik aisey gadhey par sawar they, jiski lagaam khajoor ki chhaal ki rassi ki thi, is par zeen bhi chhaal hi ki thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : hum is hadees ko sirf Muslim ki riwayat sey jantey hain jisey wo Anas sey riwayat kartey hain. aur Muslim Aa'war zaeef gardaaney jaatey hain. yehi Muslim bin Kaisaan Mulaai hain, jis par kalam kiya gaya hai, in sey Shoba aur Sufiyan ney riwayat ki hai."
1018,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki wafat hui to aap ki tadfeen key silsiley mein logon mein ikhtilaf huwa Abu-Bakar (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : mainey Rasoolullah sey eik aisi baat suni hai jo main bhoolaa nahin hun, aap ney farmaya : ''jitney bhi Nabi huye hain Allah ney un ki rooh wahin qabz ki hai jahan wo dafn kiya jana pasand kartey they (isliye) tum log unhen unkey bistar hi key maqam par dafn karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, Abdur-Rehman bin Abi Bakr Mulaiki apney hifz key talluq sey zaeef gardaaney jaatey hain. 2- ye hadees iskey ilawa tareeq sey bhi marvi (riwayat hui) hai. ibne-Abbas ney abu-Bakar Siddiq sey aur unhoney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai."
1019,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney mardon ki achchhaeyon ko zikr kiya karo aur unki buraiyan bayan karney sey baaz raho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke Imran bin Anas Makki munkirul-hadees hain. 3- baaz ney Ata sey aur Ata ney Ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey riwayat ki hai. 4- Imran bin abi Anas Misri Imran bin Anas Makki sey pehley key hain aur in sey ziyada bharosemand hain.
1020,"jab Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam kisi janaazey key sath jatey to jab tak janaza lahad (bagli qabr) mein rakh na diya jata, nahin bethtey. eik Yahudi aalim ney aap key paas aa kar kaha : Muhammad ! hum bhi aisa hi kartey hain, to Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam bethney lag gaey aur farmaya : ''tum un ki mukhalifat karo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Bishr bin Raafey hadees mein ziyada qawi nahin hain."
1021,"Mainey apney betey Sanan ko dafn kiya aur Abu-Talha khaulaani Qabr ki munder par bethtey they, jab mainey (qabr sey) nikalney ka irada kiya to wo mera haath pakad kar kaha : Abu-Sanaan ! kya main tumhen basharat na dun? mainey arz kiya : kyon nahin zarur dijiye, to unhoney kaha : mujh sey Zuhaak bin Abdur-Rehman bin Arzab ney bayan kiya ke Abu-Musa Ash-ari kehtey hain ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab bandey ka bachcha padhi. faut ho jata hai to Allah Taala apney farishton sey poochhtey hai : tum ney merey bandey key betey ki rooh qabz kar li? to wo kehtey hain : haan, phir farmata hai : tum ney uskey dil ka phal ley liya? wo kehtey hain : haan. to Allah Taala poochhtey hai : merey bandey ney kya kaha? wo kehtey hain : usney teri hamd bayan ki aur «إنا لله وإنا إليه راجعون» padha to Allah Taala farmata hai : merey bandey key liye jannat main eik ghar bana do aur uska naam baitul-hamd rakho. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan gharib hai."
1022,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Najaashi ki namaze janaza padhi to aap ney chaar takbeerein kahin. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas , ibne-Abi Aufi , Jabir , Yazeed bin Sabit aur Anas (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain 3- Yazeed bin Sabit : Zaid bin Sabit key bhai hain. ye in sey badey hain. ye Badr mein shareek they aur Zaid Badr mein shareek nahin they. 4- Sahaba kiram mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. un logon ki raey hai ke namaze-janaza mein chaar takbeerein hain. Sufiyan Sory , Malik bin Anas , ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai."
1023,"Zaid bin Arqam hamarey janaazon par chaar takbeerein kehtey they. unhoney eik janaazey par paanch takbeerein kahin hamney un sey iski wajeh poochhi, to unhoney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam aisa bhi kehtey they. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Zaid bin Arqam ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain. unka khayal hai ke janaazey mein paanch takbeerein hain. 3- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : jab Imam janaazey mein paanch takbeerein kahey to Imam ki perwi ki jaey (yani muqtadi bhi paanch kahen)."
1024,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab namaz janaza padhtey to ye dua padhtey : « اللهم اغفر لحينا وميتنا وشاهدنا وغائبنا وصغيرنا وكبيرنا وذكرنا وأنثانا » '' aey Allah ! bakhsh dey hamarey zindon ko , hamarey mardon ko , hamarey hazir ko aur hamarey ghaaieb ko , hamarey chhotey ko aur hamarey badey ko , hamarey mardon ko aur hamari aurton ko ''. Yahya bin abi Kasir kehtey hain : abu-Salma bin Abdur-Rehman ney mujh sey bayan kya ke Abu-Hurera (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi key misl riwayat ki hai. albatta is mein itna ziyada hai : اللهم من أحييته منا فأحيه على الإسلام ومن توفيته منا فتوفه على الإيمان '' aey Allah ! hum mein sey jisey to zinda rakh , usey Islam par zinda rakh aur jisey maut dey usey eman par maut dey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ابوابراہیم key walid ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. - Hisham dustwaai aur Ali bin Mubarak ney ye hadees b-tareeq : يحيى بن أبي كثير an أبي سلمة بن عبدالرحمٰن an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم mursalan riwayat ki hai, aur ikrima bin Ammar ney b-tareeq : يحيى بن أبي كثير an أبي سلمة an عائشة an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم riwayat ki hai. Ikrima bin Ammar ki hadees ghair mehfooz hai. Ikrima ko kabhi-kabhi Yahya bin abi Kasir ki hadees mein weham ho jata hai. neez ye يحيى بن أبي كثير sey (عن عبد الله بن أبي قتادة an أبيه an النبي صلى الله عليه وسلم) key tareeq sey bhi marvi hai, mainey Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari ko kehtey suna ke is silsiley mein Yahya bin abi Kasir ki hadees jisey unhoney b-tareeq : (أبي إبراهيم الأشهلي an أبيه) riwayat ki hai sab sey ziyada sahih riwayat hai, mainey un sey ابوابراہیم ka naam puchha to wo usey nahin jaan sakey , padhi. 2- is bab mein Abdur-Rehman , Aaisha , abu-Qatada , Auf bin Malik aur Jabir (Raziallahu anhu) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1025,"mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko maiyat par namaz janaza padhtey suna to mainey is par aap ki namaz sey ye kalmaat yad kiye : « اللهم اغفر له وارحمه واغسله بالبرد واغسله كما يغسل الثوب » '' aey Allah ! usey bakhsh dey, is par reham farma, usey barf sey dho dey, aur usey (gunahon sey) aisey dho dey jaisey kapdey dhoey jatey hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke us baab ki sab sey sahih yehi hadees hai."
1026,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney janaazey mein Sura Fatiha padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees ki sanad qawi nahin hai, 2- Ibrahim bin Usman hi abu-Sheba waasti hain aur wo munkirul-hadees hain. sahih chiz jo ibne-Abbas sey marvi hai ke. janaazey ki namaz mein Sura Fatiha padhna sunnat mein sey hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Umme shareek sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1027,"ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney eik namaz janaza padhaya to unhoney Sura Fatiha padhi. mainey un sey (uskey barey mein) puchha to unhoney kaha : ye sunnat hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Talha bin Abdullah bin Auf, Abdur-Rehman bin Auf key bhatijey hain. un sey Zohri ney riwayat ki hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai ye log takbire-oola key baad Sura Fatiha padhney ko pasand kartey hain yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 4- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke namaz janaza mein Sura Fatiha nahin padhi jaeygi padhi. is main to sirf Allah ki sanaa , Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam par salaat ( durood (aur maiyat key liye dua hoti hai. ehle-koofa mein sey Sory waghera ka yehi qol hai."
1028,"Malik bin Hubera (Raziallahu anhu) jab namaz janaza padhtey aur log kam hotey to unki teen safein  bana detey, phir kehtey ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya hai : ''jis ki namaze-janaza teen safon ney padhi to usney (jannat) wajib kar li ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Malik bin Hubera (Raziallahu anhu) ki hadees Hasan hai, 2- isi tarah kaee logon ney Muhammad bin Is-haq sey riwayat ki hai. Ibrahim bin Saad ney bhi ye hadees Muhammad bin Is-haq sey riwayat ki hai. aur unhoney sanad mein murtad aur Malik bin Hubera key darmiyan eik shakhs ko dakhil kar diya hai. hamarey nazdik un logon ki riwayat ziyada sahih hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Aaisha, Umme-Habiba, Abu-Hurera aur ummul-momenin Memuna (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1029,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jo musalman mar jaey aur musalmanon ki eik jamaat jiski tadaad so ko pahunchti ho uski namaz janaza padhey aur uskey liye shafaat karey to unki shafaat qubul ki jati hai''. Ali bin Hajar ney apni hadees mein kaha : « مائة فما فوقها » '' sau ya us sey zayed log ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aaisha ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- baaz ney isey moqufan riwayat kya hai, marfoo nahin kya hai."
1030,"teen ghadiyan aisi hain jin mein Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam hamen namaz padhney sey ya apney mardon ko dafnaney sey mana farmatey they : jis waqt suraj nikal raha ho yahan tak ke wo buland ho jaey, aur jis waqt theek dopehar ho rahi ho yahan tak ke suraj dhal jaey, aur jis waqt suraj doobney ki taraf maael ho yahan tak ke wo doob jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- aur Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo log un oqaat mein namaz janaza padhney ko makrooh samajhtey hain, 3- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain : is hadees mein un oqaat mein murdey dafnaney sey murad un ki namaz janaza padhna hai padhi. unhoney suraj nikaltey waqt doobtey waqt aur do-pehar key waqt jab tak ke suraj dhal na jaey namaz janaza padhney ko makrooh kaha hai. Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi isi key qaail hain, 4- Shafai kehtey hain ke in oqaat mein jin mein namaz padhna makrooh hai, un mein namaz janaza padhney mein koi harj nahin hai."
1031,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' sawari waley janaazey key peechey rahein, pedal chalney waley jahan chahey rahein, aur bachon ki bhi namaz janaza padhi jaeygi ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Israel aur deegar kaee logon ney isey Saeed bin Abdullah sey riwayat kya hai, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. ye log kehtey hain ke bachey ki namaz janaza ye jaan leney key baad ke is mein jaan dal di gaee thi padhi jaeygi bhaley hi ( wiladat key waqt ( wo roya na ho, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya usi key qaail hain padhi. ."
1032,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' bachey ki namaz ( janaza ( nahin padhi jaeygi . na wo kisi ka waris hoga aur na koi uska waris hoga jab tak ke wo paidaish key waqt roey nahin ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is hadees mein log iztirab key shikar huye hain. baaz ney isey abu Zuber sey aur abu Zuber ney Jabir sey aur Jabir ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey marfooan riwayat kya hai, aur Ash-as bin sawar aur deegar kaee logon ney abu Zuber sey aur abu Zuber ney Jabir sey moqufan riwayat ki hai, aur Muhammad bin Is-haq ney Ata bin abi Ribah sey aur Ata ney Jabir sey moqufan riwayat ki hai goya moqoof riwayat marfoo riwayat sey ziyada sahih hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke bachey ki namaz janaza nahin padhi jaeygi. jab tak ke wo paidaish key waqt na roey, yehi Sufiyan Sory aur Shafai ka qol hai."
1033,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Suhel bin Baiza ki namaz janaza masjid mein padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 3- Shafai ka bayan hai ke Malik kehtey hain : maiyat par namaz janaza masjid mein nahin padhi jaeygi, 4- Shafai kehtey hain : maiyat par namaz janaza masjid mein padhi ja sakti hai, aur unhoney isi hadees sey daleel pakdii hai."
1034,"mainey Anas bin Malik key sath eik aadmi ki namaze-janaza padhi to wo uskey sar key samney khadey huye. phir log Quraish ki eik aurat ka janaza ley kar aaye aur kaha : abu-Hamza! uski bhi namaz janaza padha diijiye, to wo chaarpaai key beech mein yani aurat ki kamar key samney khadey huye, to un sey Alaa bin Ziyad ney puchha : aap ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aurat aur mard key janaazey mein isi tarah khadey hotey dekha hai. jaisey aap khadey huye they? to unhoney kaha : haan, aur jab janazey sey farigh huye to kaha is tariqa ko yad kar lo . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki ye hadees Hasan hai, 2- aur kaee logon ney bhi hamaam sey usi key misl riwayat ki hai. Wakee ney bhi ye hadees hamaam sey riwayat ki hai, lekin unhen weham huwa hai. unhoney « an ghalib an Anas» kaha hai aur sahih « an abi ghalib » hai, Abdul-Waris bin Saeed aur deegar kaee logon ney abu-Ghalib sey riwayat ki hai jaisey hamaam ki riwayat hai, 3- is bab mein Samra sey bhi riwayat hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain. aur yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. faeyda padhi. : is hadees sey malum huwa ke aurat ki namaz janaza ho to Imam uski kamar key paas khada hoga, aur Imam ko mard key sar key bilmuqaabil khada hona chahiye kyonkey Anas bin Malik ney Abdullah bin Umer ka janaza unkey sar key paas hi khadey ho kar padhaya tha aur Alaa bin Ziyad key poochhney par unhoney kaha tha ke mainey Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko aisey hi kartey dekha hai."
1035,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik aurat padhi. ki namaz janaza padhaai, to aap uskey beech mein yani uski kamar key paas khadey huye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shoba ney bhi isey Husen Muallim sey riwayat kya hai."
1036,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Uhad key maqtooleen mein sey do do aadmiyon ko eik kapdey main eik sath kafnatey, phir poochhtey : '' un mein Quran kisey ziyada yad tha? '' to jab aap ko un mein sey kisi eik ki taraf ishara kar diya jata to aap usey lahad mein muqaddam rakhtey aur farmatey : '' qiyamat key roz mein un logon par gawah rahunga ''. aur aap ney unhen unkey khoon hi mein dafnaney ka hukm diya aur un ki namaz janaza nahin padhi aur na hi unhen ghusl hi diya . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Jabir ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, ye hadees Zohri sey marvi hai unhoney usey Anas sey aur Anas ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai neez ye Zohri sey Abdullah bin Solba bin abi Saeer key wastey sey bhi marvi hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai aur un mein sey baaz ney isey Jabir ki riwayat sey zikr kya, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas bin Malik sey bhi riwayat hai, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka shaheed ki namaz janaza key silsiley mein ikhtilaf hai. baaz kehtey hain ke shaheed ki namaz janaza nahin padhi jaeygi . yehi ehal Madina ka qol hai. Shafai aur Ahmed bhi yehi kehtey hain, 4- aur baaz kehtey hain ke shaheed ki namaz padhi jaeygi. un logon ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki hadees sey daleel pakdi hai ke aap ney Hamza (Raziallahu anhu) ki namaz padhi thi. Sory aur ehle-koofa isi key qaail hain aur yehi Is-haq bin Raahviya bhi kehtey hain."
1037,"mujhey eik aisey shakhs ney khabar di hai jisney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko dekha ke aap ney eik qabr alag thalag dekhi to apney peechey Sahaba ki saf-bandi ki aur uski namaze-janaza padhaai. Shaaby sey puchha gaya ke aap ko ye khabar kis ney di? to unhoney kaha : ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ney. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Anas , Barida, Yazeed bin Sabit , abu-Huraira, Aamir bin Rabeea, abu-Qatada aur Sehal bin Hanif sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. yehi Shafai, Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain ke qabr par namaz padhi jaeygi padhi. ye Malik bin Anas ka qol hai, 5- Abdullah bin Mubarak kehtey hain ke jab maiyat ko dafn kar diya jaey aur uski namaz janaza na padhi gaee ho to uski namaz janaza qabr par padhi jaeygi, 6- ibne-Mubarak qabr par namaz ( janaza ( padhney key qaail hain, 7- Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya kehtey hain : qabr par namaz eik maah tak padhi ja sakti hai. ye kehtey hain ke hamney aksar suna hai Saeed bin Musaiyab sey riwayat hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney Saad bin Ubada ki walida ki namaz janaza eik maah key baad qabr par padhi."
1038,"Umme Saad ka intiqal ho gaya aur Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam mojud nahin they, jab aap tashrif laye to unki namaz janaza padhi. is waqiey ko eik maah guzar chuka tha."
1039,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney hum logon sey farmaya : '' tumharey bhai najashi ka intiqal ho gaya hai. tum log utho aur unki namaz janaza padho''. to ham khadey huye aur saf-bandi ki, jaisey maiyat key liye ki jati hai''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees is sanad sey Hasan sahih gharib hai, 2- ye hadees abu-Qulaba ney bhi apney chacha abu-Mohlab sey aur unhoney Imran bin Husain sey riwayat ki hai, 3- abu-Mohlab ka naam Abdur-Rehman bin Amr hai. unhen Muawiya bin Amr bhi kaha jata hai, 4- is bab mein abu-Huraira, Jabir bin Abdullah, abu-Saeed , Huzefa bin Usaid aur Jareer bin Abdullah (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1040,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jisney koi namaz janaza padhi , uskey liye eik qeeraat sawab hai. aur jo uskey sath rahey yahan tak ke uski tadfeen mukammal kar li jaey to uskey liye do qeeraat sawab hai, un mein sey eik qeeraat ya un mein sey chhota qeeraat Uhad key barabar hoga''. to mainey ibne-Umar sey uska zikr kya to unhoney mujhey ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) key paas bheja aur un sey us barey mein puchhwaya to unhoney kaha : Abu-Hurera sach kehtey hain. to ibne-Umar ney kaha : hamney bahut sey qeeraat ganwa diye . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- un sey kaee sanadon sey ye marvi hai, padhi. 3- is bab mein Bara, Abdullah bin Mughaffal, Abdullah bin Masood, abu Saeed Khudri , Ubai-bin Kaab , ibne-Umar aur Soban (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1041,"mainey abu-Muhazzim ko kehtey suna ke main das saal Abu-Hurera key sath raha . mainey unhen suna , wo keh rahey they ke mainey Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna hai : '' jo kisi janaazey key sath gaya aur usey teen baar kandha diya to, usney apna haq pura kar diya jo is par tha''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai, 2- isey baaz ney isi sanad sey riwayat kya hai lekin isey marfoo nahin kya hai, 3- abu-Muhazzim ka naam Yazeed bin Sufiyan hai. Shoba ney unhen zaeef kaha hai."
1042,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jab tum janaza dekho to khadey ho jaya karo yahan tak ke wo tumhen chhod kar aagey nikal jaey ya rakh diya jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Aamir bin Rabeea ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , Jabir , Suhel bin Hanif , Qais bin Saad aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1043,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab tum janaza dekho to uskey liye khadey ho jaya karo . aur jo uskey sath jaey wo hergiz na bethey jab tak ke janaza rakh na diya jaey ''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- abu Saeed Khudri ki hadees is baab mein Hasan sahih hai, 2- yehi Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai. ye kehtey hain ke jo kisi janaazey key sath jaey, wo hergiz na bethey jab tak ke janaza logon ki gardanon sey utaar kar rakh na diya jaey, padhi. 3- Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey baaz ehle-ilm sey marvi hai ke wo janaazey key aagey jatey they aur janaza pahunchney sey pehley beth jatey they. aur yehi Shafai ka qol hai."
1044,"un sey janaazey key liye jab tak ke wo rakh na diya jaey khadey rehney ka zikr kya gaya to Ali ney kaha : Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam khadey rehtey they phir aap bethney lagey they . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- is mein chaar Tabe-een ki riwayat hai jo eik doosrey sey riwayat kar rahey hain, 3- Shafai kehtey hain : is baab mein ye sab sey ziyada sahih riwayat hai, ye hadees pehli hadees '' jab tum janaza dekho , to khadey ho jaao '' ki naasikh hai, 4- is bab mein Hasan bin Ali aur ibne-Abbas sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 5- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai, 6- Ahmed kehtey hain ke chahey to khada ho jaey aur chahey to khada na ho. unhoney is baat sey daleel pakdi hai ke Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key barey mein marvi hai ke aap khadey ho jaya kartey they phir bethey rehney lagey . isi tarah Is-haq bin Ibrahim bin Raahviya ka bhi qol hai, 7- Ali (Raziallahu anhu) key qol ( Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam janaazey key liye khadey ho jaya kartey they phir aap bethey rehney lagey ka mafhoom ye hai ke Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab janaza dekhtey to khadey ho jatey phir baad mein aap us sey ruk gaey . jab koi janaza dekhtey to khadey nahin hotey ( ."
1045,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' baghli qabr hamarey liye hai aur sanduqi qabr auron key liye hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees us tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jareer bin Abdullah , Aaisha , ibne-Umar aur Jabir (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1046,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam jab maiyat qabr mein dakhil kar di jati (aur kabhi Raavi hadees abu-Khalid kehtey ( jab maiyat apni qabr mein rakh di jati to aap kabhi : (بسم الله وبالله وعلى ملة رسول الله) padhtey aur kabhi (بسم الله وبالله وعلى سنة رسول الله صلى الله عليه وسلم)'' Allah key naam sey, Allah ki madad sey aur Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key tariqa par mein usey qabr mein rakhta hun '' padhtey . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees us tareeq sey Hasan gharib hai, 2- ye hadees doosrey tareeq sey bhi ibne-Umar sey marvi hai, unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey riwayat ki hai aur usey abu-Siddiq naaji ney bhi ibne-Umar sey riwayat kya hai aur unhoney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey , 3- neez ye Siddiq naji key wastey sey ibne-Umar sey bhi moqufan marvi hai."
1047,"mainey Jaafar bin Muhammad sey suna wo apney baap sey riwayat kar rahey they jis aadmi ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qabr baghli banai , wo abu-Talha hain aur jisney aap key nichey chadar bichhaai wo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key Mola Shuqran hain, Jaafar kehtey hain : aur mujhey Ubedullah bin abi Raafey ney khabar di wo kehtey hain ke mainey Shuqran ko kehtey suna : Allah ki qism ! mainey qabr mein Rasoolullah key nichey chadar padhi. bichhaai thi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Shuqran ki hadees Hasan gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas sey bhi riwayat hai,"
1048,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ki qabr main eik lal chadar rakhi gaee . aur Muhammad bin Bashaar ney dusri jagah is sanad mein abu-Jamra kaha hai aur ye ziyada sahih hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- Shoba ney abu-Hamza qassaab sey bhi riwayat ki hai, unka naam Imran bin abi ata hai, aur abu-Jamra Zabee sey bhi riwayat ki gaee hai, unka naam Nasar bin Imran hai. ye dono ibne-Abbas key shagrid hain, 3- ibne-Abbas sey ye bhi riwayat ki gaee hai ke unhoney qabr mein maiyat key nichey kisi chiz key bichaney ko makrooh jana hai. baaz ehle-ilm isi taraf gaey hain."
1049,"Ali (Raziallahu anhu) ney abul-Yahaj Asadi sey kaha : main tumhen eik aisey kaam key liye bhej raha hun jis key liye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney mujhey bheja tha : '' tum jo bhi ubhri qabr ho, usey barabar kiye baghair aur jo bhi mujassama ho, usey mismaar kiye baghair na chhodna''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ali ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir sey bhi riwayat hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo qabr ko zamin sey buland rakhney ko makruh (tehreemi) qarar detey hain, 4- Shafai kehtey hain ke qabr key oonchi kiye janey ko mein makruh (tehrimi) siwaye itni miqdaar key jis sey malum ho sakey ke ye qabr hai taake wo na rondi jaey aur na is par betha jaey."
1050,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''qabron par na betho padhi. aur na unhen samney kar key namaz padho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : is baab mein abu-Huraira, Amr bin hazam aur Bashir bin khasasiya sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1051,"abu-Murshid ghanwi (Raziallahu anhu) ney Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey isi tarah riwayat ki hai. albatta is sanad mein abu-Idrees ka wasta nahin hai aur yehi sahih hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : Muhammad bin Ismail Bukhari kehtey hain ke ibne-Mubarak ki riwayat ghalat hai, is mein ibne-Mubarak sey ghalati hui hai unhoney is mein abu-Idrees khaulaani ka wasta badha diya hai, sahih ye hai ke basar bin Abdullah ney baghair wastey key baraahe-raast Waasila sey riwayat ki hai, isi tarah kaee aur logon ney Abdur-Rehman bin Yazeed bin Jabir sey riwayat ki hai aur is mein abu-Idrees key wastey ka zikr nahin hai. aur Basar bin Abdullah ney Waasila Isqaa sey suna hai."
1052,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney is baat sey mana farmaya hai ke qabren pukhta ki jaeyn, un par likha jaey padhi. aur un par imarat banai jaey padhi. aur unhen raunda jaey. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, 2- ye aur bhi turq sey Jabir sey marvi hai, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ney qabron par mitti dalney ki ijazat di hai, unhi mein sey Hasan Basri bhi hain, 4- Shafai kehtey hain : qabron par mitti dalney mein koi harj nahin hai."
1053,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam Madiney ki chand qabron key paas sey guzrey, to unki taraf rukh kar key aap ney farmaya : « السلام عليكم يا أهل القبور يغفر الله لنا ولكم أنتم سلفنا ونحن بالأثر » ''salamti ho tum par aey qabr walo! Allah hamen aur tumhen bakhshey tum hamarey pesh ro ho aur hum bhi tumharey peechey aaney waley hain''. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas Raziallahu anhuma ki hadees gharib hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Barida (Raziallahu anhu) aur Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1054,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''main ney tumhen qabron ki ziyaarat sey roka tha. ab Muhammad ko apni maa ki qabr ki ziyaarat ki ijazat dey di gaee hai. to tum bhi un ki ziyaarat karo, ye chiz aakhirat ko yad dilati hai'' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Barida ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein abu Saeed Khudri , ibne-Masood , Anas , Abu-Hurera aur Umme-Salma (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, padhi. 3- ehle-ilm ka isi par amal hai. wo qabron ki ziyaarat mein koi harj nahin samajhtey. ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya usi key qaail hain."
1055,"Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakar Habsha mein wafat paa gaey to unhen Makka la kar dafn kya gaya, jab ummul-momenin Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ( Makka ( aain to Abdur-Rehman bin abi Bakr (Raziallahu anhu) ki qabr par aa kar unhoney ye ashaar padhey وكنا كندماني جذيمة حقبة من الدهر حتى قيل لن يتصدعا فلما تفرقنا كأني ومالكا لطول اجتماع لم نبت ليلة معا'' hum dono eik arsey tak eik sath aisey rahey they jaisey badshah Jazeema key do saathi yahan tak ke ye kaha janey laga ke ye dono kabhi eik doosrey sey juda na hongey. phir jab hum juda huye to muddat daraz tak eik sath rehney key bawajud aisa lagney laga goya main aur Malik eik raat bhi kabhi eik sath na rahey hon''. phir kaha : Allah ki qasam! agar main tumharey paas mojud hoti to tujhey wahin dafn kya jata jahan tera intiqal huwa aur agar main hazir rahi hoti to teri ziyaarat ko na aati."
1056,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney qabron ki ziyada ziyaarat karney wali aurton par lanat bheji hai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein ibne-Abbas aur Hassan bin Sabit sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke ye Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key qabron ki ziyaarat ki ijazat deney sey pehley ki baat hai. jab aap ney uski ijazat de-di to ab us ijazat mein mard aur aurten dono shamil hain, 4- baaz kehtey hain ke aurton key liye qabron ki ziyaarat un ki qillat sabr aur kasrat roney-dhoney ki wajeh sey makrooh hai."
1057,"Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam eik qabr mein raat ko dakhil huye to aap key liye eik chiragh roshan kya gaya۔ aap ney maiyat ko qibley ki taraf sey liya. aur farmaya : Allah tum par reham kerey! tum bahut naram dil roney waley, aur bahut ziyada Quran ki tilawat karney waley they. aur aap ney is par chaar takbeerein kahin . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ibne-Abbas ki hadees Hasan hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein Jabir aur Yazeed bin Sabit sey bhi ahadees aai hain aur Yazeed bin Sabit , Zaid bin Sabit key bhai hain, aur un sey badey hain, 3- baaz ehle-ilm usi taraf gaey hain, wo kehtey hain ke maiyat ko qabr mein qibley ki taraf sey utara jaeyga padhi. , 4- baaz kehtey hain : paaytaney ki taraf sey rakh kar khinch leingey padhi. , 5- aur aksar ehle-ilm ney raat ko dafn karney ki ijazat di hai."
1058,"Rasoolullah key paas sey eik janaza guzra , logon ney uski tareef ki padhi. to Rasulullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' ( jannat ( wajib ho gaee '' phir farmaya : '' tum log zamin par Allah key gawah ho '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Anas ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Kaab bin Ajra aur Abu-Hurera (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain."
1059,"main Madiney aaya, to umr bin Khattab (Raziallahu anhu) key paas aa kar betha itney mein kuch log eik janaza ley kar guzrey to logon ney uski tareef ki umr (Raziallahu anhu) ney kaha : wajib ho gaee , mainey umr (Raziallahu anhu) sey puchha : kya chiz wajib ho gaee? to unhoney kaha : main wohi baat keh raha hun jo Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney kahi hai. aap ney farmaya : ''jis kisi bhi musalman key ( nek honey ki) teen aadmi gawahi den, uskey liye jannat wajib ho gaee ''. hamney arz kya : agar do aadmi gawahi den ? aap ney farmaya : '' do aadmi bhi '' hamney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey eik ki gawahi key barey mein nahin puchha . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1060,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : '' jis musalman key teen bachey faut ho jaeyn usey jahannam ki aag nahin chhueygi magar qism puri karney key liye '' padhi. . Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai, padhi. 2- is bab mein umr , Muaz , Kaab bin Malik , Utba bin abd , Umme Sulem , Jabir , Anas , Abu-Zar , ibne-Masood , abu-Solba Ashjai, ibne-Abbas, Aqba bin Aamir , abu Saeed Khudri aur Qara bin Ayas Muzni (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi ahadees aai hain, 3- abu-Soba Ashjai ki Nabi akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey sirf eik hi hadees hai, aur wo yehi hadees hai, aur ye khushnii nahin hain ( Abu-Solba khushnii doosrey hain ( ."
1061,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney teen bachchon ko (ladkey hon ya ladkiyan) bator zakhira aakhirat key aagey bhej diya ho, aur wo baaligha umr ko na pahunchey hon to wo uskey liye jahannam sey bachaney ka eik mazbut qil'a hongey.'' is par Abu-Zar (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : mainey do bachchey bhejey hain? aap ney farmaya : ''do bhi kafi hain.'' to Ubai-bin Kaab Saiyedul-Qurraa (Raziallahu anhu) ney arz kiya : mainey eik hi bheja hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''eik bhi kafi hai. albatta ye qil'a us waqt hongey jab wo pehley sadmey key waqt yani marney key sath hi sabr karey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- Abu-Ubaida ney apney walid Abdullah bin Masood (Raziallahu anhu) sey nahin suna hai."
1062,"Unhoney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey suna : ''meri ummat mein sey jis key do paish-rau hon, Allah usey unki wajeh sey jannat mein dakhil karega.'' is par Aaisha (Raziallahu Anha) ney arz kiya : aap ki ummat mein sey jis key eik hi paish-rau ho to? aap ney farmaya : ''jis key eik hi paish-rau ho usey bhi, aey tofiq-yafta khatoon !'' (phir) unhoney puchha : aap ki ummat mein jis ka koi paish-rau hi na ho uska kya hoga? to aap ney farmaya : ''main apni ummat ka paish-rau hun kisi ki judai sey unhen aisi takleef nahin hogi jaisi meri judai sey unhen hogi.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- hum isey Abde-Rabba bin Baariq hi ki riwayat sey jantey hain aur un sey kaee Aaimma ney riwayat ki hai."
1063,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''shaheed paanch log hain : jo taaoon mein mara ho, jo pet key marz sey mara ho, jo doob kar mara ho, jo deewar waghera gir janey sey mara ho, aur jo Allah ki raah mein shaheed huwa ho.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Anas , Safwan bin Umayya , Jabir bin Ateek, Khalid bin Arfataa, Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Surad, Abu-Musa Ash-ari aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1064,Suleman (Alaihissalam) bin Surad ney Khalid bin Arfataa sey (ya Khalid ney Suleman (Alaihissalam) sey) puchha : kya aap ney Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ko farmatey nahin suna? jisey uska pet maar dey padhi. usey qabr mein azab nahin diya jaeyga to un mein sey eik ney apney doosrey sathi sey kaha : haan (suna hai). Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- is baab mein ye hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- iskey ilawa ye aur bhi tareeq sey marvi (riwayat hui) hai.
1065,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney taaoon ka zikr kiya, to farmaya : ''ye us azab ka bacha huwa hissey hai, jo Bani-Israel key eik giroh padhi. par bheja gaya tha jab kisi zamin (mulk ya shehar) mein taaoon ho jahan par tum reh rahey ho to wahan sey na niklo padhi. aur jab wo kisi aisi sar zamin mein phela ho jahan tum na rehtey ho to wahan na jaao.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Usama bin Zaid ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Saad , Khuzaima bin Sabit , Abdur-Rehman bin Auf , Jabir aur Aaisha sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1066,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Allah sey milna chahta hai Allah bhi us sey milna chahta hai aur jo Allah sey milney ko napasand karta ho Allah bhi us sey milney ko napasand karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Ubada bin Samit ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein abu-Musa Ash-ari , Abu-Hurera , aur Aaisha (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1067,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo Allah sey milna chahta hai Allah bhi us sey milna chahta hai, aur jo Allah sey milney ko napasand karta hai Allah bhi us sey milney ko napasand karta hai.'' to mainey arz kiya : Allah key Rasool ! hum sabhi ko maut napasand hai? to aap ney farmaya : ''ye murad nahin hai, balke murad ye hai ke momin ko jab Allah ki rehmat, uski khushnoodi aur uskey jannat ki basharat di jati hai to wo Allah sey milna chahta hai aur Allah us sey milna chahta hai, aur kafir ko jab Allah key azab aur uske ghussey ki khabar di jati hai to wo Allah sey milney ko napasand karta hai aur Allah bhi us sey milney ko napasand karta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1068,"Eik shakhs ney khudkushi kar li, to Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney uski namaze janaza nahin padhi. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is masley mein ehle-ilm ka ikhtilaf hai, baaz kehtey hain ke har shakhs ki namaz padhi jaeygi jo qibley ki taraf namaz padhta ho aur khudkushi karney waley ki bhi padhi jaeygi. Sauri aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka yehi qol hai. 3- aur Ahmed kehtey hain : Imam khudkushi karney waley ki namaz nahin padheiga, albatta (musalmanon key musalman haakim) Imam key ilawa log padhengey."
1069,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas eik shakhs laya gaya taake aap uski namaze-janaza padhaaen to aap Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''tum apney sathi ki namaz padh lo kyonkey is par qarz hai.'' (Main nahin padhunga) is par Abu-Qatada ney arz kiya : uski adaegi merey zimmey hai, Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney puchha : ''pura-pura ada karogey?'' to unhoney kaha : (haan) pura-pura ada karengey to aap ney uski namaze-janaza padhaai. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Qatada ki hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- is bab mein Jabir , Salma bin Akwaa , Asma binte Yazeed (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain."
1070,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam key paas koi faut shuda shakhs (maiyat) jis par qarz ho laya jata to aap poochhtey : ''kya is ney apney qarz ki adaegi key liye kuchh chhoda hai?'' agar aap ko bataya jata ke usney itna maal chhoda hai jis sey uskey qarz ki mukammal adaegi ho jaeygi to aap uski namaze-janaza padhatey, warna musalmanon sey farmatey : ''tum log apney sathi ki namaze-janaza padh lo (main nahin padh sakta).''  phir jab Allah ney aap key liye futoohaat ka darwaza khola to aap khadey huye aur aap ney farmaya : ''main musalmanon ka unki apni janon sey ziyada haqdaar hun. to musalmanon mein sey jiski maut ho jaey aur wo qarz chhod jaey to uski adaegi merey zimma hai aur jo koi maal chhod kar jaey to wo uskey warison ka hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan sahih hai. 2- usey Yahya bin Buker aur deegar kaee logon ney Les bin Saad sey Abdullah bin Saleh ki hadees ki tarah riwayat kiya hai."
1071,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab maiyat ko ya tum mein sey kisi ko dafna diya jata hai to uskey paas kaley rang ki neeli aankh waley do farishtey aatey hain, un mein sey eik ko Munkir aur doosrey ko Nakeer kaha jata hai. aur wo dono poochhtey hain : to us shakhs key barey mein kya kehta tha. wo (maiyat) kehta hai : wohi jo wo khud kehtey they ke wo Allah key bandey aur Allah key Rasool hain, aur main gawahi deta hun ke Allah key siwa koi mabood bar-haq nahin aur Muhammad Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam uskey bandey aur Rasool hain to wo dono kehtey hain : hamein malum tha ke to yehi kaheyga phir uski qabr lambaae aur chaudaai mein satar-satar gaz kushada kar di jati hai, phir is mein roshni kar di jati hai. phir us sey kaha jata hai : so ja, wo kehta hai : mujhey merey ghar walon key paas wapis pahuncha do ke main unhen ye bata sakoon, to wo dono kehtey hain : to so ja us dulhan ki tarah jisey sirf wohi jagaata hai jo uskey ghar walon mein usey sab sey ziyada mehbub hota hai, yahan tak ke Allah usey uski us khuwab gaah sey uthaey, aur agar wo munafiq hai, to kehta hai : main logon ko jo kehtey sunta tha, wohi main bhi kehta tha aur mujhey kuchh nahin maloom. to wo dono us sey kehtey hain : hamein malum tha ke to yehi kaheyga phir zamin sey kaha jata hai : to isey daboch ley to wo isey daboch leti hai aur phir uski pasliyan idhar ki udhar ho jati hain. wo hamesha isi azab mein mubtala rehta hai. yahan tak ke Allah usey uski us khuwab gaah sey uthaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- Abu-Hurera ki hadees Hasan gharib hai. 2- is bab mein Ali , Zaid bin Sabit, ibne-Abbas , Bara bin Aazib , abu-Ayyub , Anas , Jabir , Ummul-momenin Aaisha aur Abu-Sufiyaan (Raziallauh anhum) sey bhi hadeesen aai hain. un sabhon ney Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam sey azabe-qabr key mutalliq riwayat ki hai."
1072,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jab koi aadmi martaa hai to is par subah aur Sham uska thikana pesh kiya jata hai, agar wo jannatiyon mein sey hai to jannat mein apna thikana dekhta hai aur agar wo jahannamiyon mein sey hai to wo jahannam mein apna thikana dekhta hai, phir us sey kaha jata hai : ye tera thikana hai, yahan tak ke Allah tujhey qiyamat key din uthaey.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : ye hadees Hasan sahih hai."
1073,"Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi musibat zada ki musibat mein uska haal-chaal puchha to, usey bhi uskey barabar ajr milega (jitna ki use musibat par sabr karne par milta hai).'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf Ali bin Aasim ki riwayat sey marfoo jantey hain, baaz logon ney Muhammad bin Suqa sey isi jaisi hadees isi sanad sey moqufan riwayat ki hai. aur isey marfoo nahin kiya hai. 3- kaha jata hai ke Ali bin Aasim par jo ziyada ta'ana maara gaya, aur logon ney un par nakeer ki hai wo isi hadees key sabab hai."
1074,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jo musalman Jume key din ya Jume ki raat ko martaa hai, Allah usey qabr key fitney sey mehfooz rakhta hai.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- is hadees ki sanad muttasil nahin hai, Rabeea bin Saif abu-Abdur-Rehman Habli sey riwayat kartey hain aur wo Abdullah bin Amr sey. aur hum nahin jantey ke Rabeea bin Saif ki Abdullah bin Amr Raziallahu anhuma sey samaa (suna), hai ya nahin."
1075,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney un sey farmaya : ''Ali ! teen chizon mein der na karo : namaz ko jab uska waqt ho jaey, janaze ko jab aa jaey, aur bewa (ke nikah) ko jab tum uska kufu (munasib hamsar) paa lo.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- main iski sanad muttasil nahin janta."
1076,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''jisney kisi aisi aurat ki ta'ziyat (maatam pursi) ki jiska ladka mar gaya ho, to usey jannat mein iskey badle eik umda kapda pehnaya jaeyga.'' Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- iski sanad qawi nahin hai."
1077,"Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney eik janaazey mein Allahu-Akbar kaha to pehli takbir par aap ney rafaa-yadein kiya aur daayan haath baaein hath key ooper rakha. Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees gharib hai. 2- hum isey sirf isi tareeq sey jantey hain. 3- ehle-ilm ka is masle mein ikhtilaf hai, Sahaba kiram waghaira mein sey aksar ehle-ilm ka khayal hai ke aadmi janaazey mein har takbir key waqt dono haath uthaeyga, ye ibne-Mubarak , Shafai , Ahmed aur Is-haq bin Raahviya ka qol hai. 4- baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : sirf pehli baar apney dono haath uthaey ga. yehi Sauri aur ehle-Koofa ka qol hai. 5- ibne-Mubarak kehtey hain ke namaze-janaza mein dahiney haath sey apney baaein hath ko nahin pakdeyga. 6- aur baaz ehle-ilm kehtey hain : wo apney dahiney haath sey apney baaein hath ko pakdeyga jaisey wo dusri namaz mein karta hai.  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : haath baandhnaa mujhey ziyada pasand hai."
1078,Rasoolullah Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ki jaan uskey qarz ki wajeh sey atki rehti hai jab tak ke uski adaegi na ho jaey.''
1079,Abu-Huraira (Raziallahu anhu) sey riwayat hai ke Nabi Akram Sallallahu Alehi w aalehi wasallam ney farmaya : ''momin ki jaan uskey qarz ki wajeh sey atki rehti padhi. hai jab tak ke uski adaegi na ho jaey.''  Imam Tirmizi kehtey hain : 1- ye hadees Hasan hai. 2- ye pehli hadees sey ziyada sahih hai.
